irst place and I'll book with Expedia, which will save me a ton of hassle. I'm looking forward to seeing my money in the coming days!! All in all, I probably wouldn't stay here on principal again, would I recommend it to my best friend? Maybe if they got a great price with Expedia and didn't mind a bit of noise. I don't have anything to compare it to in SF but I would probably try something else next time.Oh, and the beefeaters are probably the most useless gimmick I've ever seen - they were completely unfriendly and hardly ever there anyway...	
